{"tid":1082353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大峽谷跌死個男人原來係澳門人","createTime":"2019-03-29T01:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T16:09:09.000Z","uid":23707,"like":195,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"bfad956f58a4e88053204c39a34b7a808cccf149","tid":1082353,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"澳門男遊美大峽谷失足墮斃 旅議會指死者獨自報康泰團<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/bkn-20190329092424848-0329_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fbkn-20190329092424848-0329_00822_001.html&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85Hfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=88ae7071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/bkn-20190329092424848-0329_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一名在香港報團的50多歲澳門男子，周四(28日)在美國著名景點大峽谷墮崖死亡，香港旅遊業議會總幹事陳張樂怡表示，收到康泰旅行社報告，證實死者是一個7天團的團友，他單獨報團，在3月26日出發，於當地周四早上參加自費活動，在天空步道附近的老鷹崖自拍時墮崖，當時有領隊在場。由於事主有買保險，旅行社及保險公司會協助處理其後事，而據了解澳門的旅遊危機處理辦公室亦正跟進事件。"},{"pid":"b595d4733a16c628f2a5fc70bdad6ff3ed3fbd4a","tid":1082353,"uid":188418,"like":325,"dislike":6,"score":319,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:22:47.000Z","msg":"單獨報團 好撚sad"},{"pid":"9ce8beef6e873ceccc2a41175048d1ca24a5f355","tid":1082353,"uid":134474,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"996dfcb3a15934177b8b6599bbbb8a174c527490","tid":1082353,"uid":28195,"like":66,"dislike":7,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"係咪中共黨員呀，又黎被自殺"},{"pid":"4456943f3f096c71f11aae39ead9a4e784220dce","tid":1082353,"uid":163350,"like":28,"dislike":63,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1643227391e32286740f5575c223744ca8c950e","tid":1082353,"uid":2772,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"咁就撚死囉"},{"pid":"79904fa8a1775f6c4ebd480b257de1719f82289d","tid":1082353,"uid":38548,